      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''The debt relief issue is now a speeding train. We've got the pope and every missionary in the world involved in this thing, and they persuaded just about everyone here that this is the noble thing to do.''</p>
        <p>REPRESENATIVE SONNY CALLAHAN, on a Congressional deal to forgive poor nations' debts. [A12]</p>
